{% extends "base.html" %}

{% block title %}FAQ{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h2 class="sports">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<ol id="faq">
	<li> Where are we?<p>We are located in Canal Avenue, Mullingar, Co Westmeath, Ireland. (see <a href="/Contact">find us</a> page for directions on all transport options)</p></li>
	
	<li>How do I contact you for info, bookings etc?<p>Simply call (044) 931 3000 or visit our <a href="/Contact">contact</a> page for other options</p></li>
	
	<li>How can I pay?	<p>We accept all types of payment including cash, laser, Visa, Visa Debit & MasterCard. Payment is required before you start the circuit.</p></li>
	
	<li>Is there physical contact with other competitors?<p>No this is a skill based activity with no physical contact and little physical exertion required.</p></li>
	
	<li>Is there age limits for this activity?<p>This activity is designed for adults and children from 8 years and upwards.</p>
	</li>

	<li>What clothing is required?<p>No special clothing or sports gear is needed, something comfortable to allow free movement when shooting at targets and soft sole runners. All sports equipment is provided by Kingdom of Sports</p></li>	
	
	<li>How much does it cost?
		<p>Regular customers will pay for 1.5 hours of sports activity entertainment 10 euro off-peak & 15 euro during peak hours.
		 We also have package deals for groups and events so please refer to our pricing section <a href="/Pricing">here</a>.</p>	
	</li>

	<li>What are the opening hours of Kingdom of Sports
		<p>Kingdom of Sports is open from 12pm - 8pm daily. Last entry into the arena is at 7pm.</p>	
	</li>
	
	<li>
		Are there any other facilities on site?
		<p>Yes we have our comfortable Arena Cafe with views of the Sports Arena</p>
		<ul id="faq-facilities">
			<li>Pool Table</li>
			<li>Big Screens</li>
			<li>Toilets & baby changing facilities</li>
			<li>Merchandise shop</li>
			<li>Music</li>
			<li>Art, Crafts & Drama classes of various levels available on request for groups</li>
		</ul>	
	</li>
	<br/>
	<li>How many people can you cater for? <p>The circuit can accommodate 80 in an hour while we can entertain much more with our other facilities as above.</p></li>


</ol>
{% endblock %}